data.description: You will love this spacious three-bed, two-and-a-half-bath home on a GREENBELT!  Featuring an inviting open floor plan with upgraded lighting plus and oversized fan added to the downstairs living space for comfort, and the beautiful epoxy-coated garage floor for durability and ease of use.  The primary bedroom's spacious walk-in closet has been customized to fulfill your wildest dreams! The subdivision offers quick access to 1604 via Shaenfield and the conveniences of Alamo Ranch and Culebra via FM1560.  Children in the neighborhood receive top-notch educations from esteemed NISD Schools! Homes like this with large bedrooms, a spacious fully-fenced backyard, plus a kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances with included refrigerator typically sell quickly, so you are encouraged to schedule your showing asap! [Grass has been digitally greened]
